text: Kalajoki is a town in Northern Ostrobothnia, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 12,328 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Alavieska, Kokkola, Kannus, Merijärvi, Pyhäjoki, Sievi and Ylivieska. == Other websites == * Town of Kalajoki – Official website * Kalajoki Tourism Information Category:Towns in Finland Category:Municipalities of North Ostrobothnia
